data.description: Walk to Lake Nottely from your ship-inspired home! Convenient to downtown Blairsville, this 3 BR/2.5 BA home is filled with natural light through big round windows! Enter this home into a spacious kitchen stocked with up-to-date appliances and abundant cabinet space. 2 BR are located on the main floor with a laundry room and full bathroom. The master suite encompasses the loft area with a private deck to enjoy the fresh mountain air and the surrounding foliage! A full partially finished basement has loads of storage space and includes a half bath! Outdoor spaces include a fenced back yard, and full deck patiently waiting for your guests! Oh yeah, it's only a mile from a marina on Lake Nottely!
